1
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,200
{\an8}Hello?

2
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:46,720
{\an8}So it was you
who helped your dad and Techut.

3
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:49,680
{\an8}We have to lure Damon out and unmask him.

4
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:59,640
{\an8}<i>The virus is a weapon</i>
<i>that can destroy our enemies,</i>

5
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:02,000
{\an8}so why don't we use it to our advantage?

6
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,600
{\an8}NARUBAN AND THE NEXT STEP OF 3C

7
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:18,280
{\an8}<i>Our company got scammed!</i>

8
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,400
The CEO here, his name's Narubodee.

9
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:22,520
He stole our money and gave it to his son,

10
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,120
that bastard, Naruban.

11
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,680
Dad! Mom!

12
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:32,360
Take good care of yourself, Giranun.

13
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,280
Your dad and I really have to do this.

14
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,200
- Mom!
- Giranun!

15
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,440
Remember,

16
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,720
take your revenge.
Make sure they fall like us!

17
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,840
Dad, don't. Please don't do this.
Don't leave me.

18
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,640
Go after Naruban!

19
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,600
Dad!

20
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,280
Dad…

21
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:21,640
<i>My parents killed themselves</i>
<i>because of your family.</i>

22
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:24,080
<i>It's time you paid</i>
<i>for their lives with yours,</i>

23
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,600
<i>Naruban.</i>

24
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,520
I've tried every way

25
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:35,080
and everything to get close to you,

26
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,320
Naruban.

27
00:04:58,400 --> 00:04:59,360
Nun.

28
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:03,320
Nun, what's wrong?

29
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,960
Nun!

30
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,840
Why are you all bruised up?

31
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,640
What's wrong? What happened?

32
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:13,160
Mom captured me.

33
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,360
Giranun captured you?

34
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:20,360
She chooses Punlop over her own family.

35
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:27,600
How could she do this to our family?

36
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,640
What? Nun!

37
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:43,720
It's my fault.

38
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,480
I never cared about anyone's feelings.

39
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,840
All I did was give orders.

40
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:53,240
I've been so self-centered.

41
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,800
Even when I teach you,

42
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:59,120
I teach you to exploit others
and to be selfish.

43
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:03,280
That's why our home doesn't feel like one.

44
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,080
It feels more like hell.

45
00:06:12,440 --> 00:06:13,360
Nun.

46
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,520
Te.

47
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,280
I'm sorry.

48
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:25,160
I'm sorry for putting your lives at risk.

49
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:30,120
And I'm sorry for raising you so poorly.

50
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,560
I've been a horrible son.

51
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:46,000
I kept causing you trouble.

52
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,160
Listen.

53
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,040
I'll help Taiga.

54
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:01,160
We need to stop the virus.

55
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,880
Dad.

56
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:09,440
I'll testify to expose Fire Phoenix
as a secret society.

57
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:14,080
At 3C, we've laundered money for them
for far too long.

58
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:15,640
Secret society?

59
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:20,640
Fire Phoenix ordered us to create a virus.

60
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,040
Dad.

61
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,840
If you talk about the virus,

62
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,400
you'll go to jail.

63
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,680
And you'll die in jail.

64
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,040
I need to take responsibility for it.

65
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:42,200
My word carries the most weight.

66
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,840
It can be used as evidence.

67
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,320
No way, Dad.

68
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,440
You can't go to jail.

69
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:56,680
I will testify that I made
all the decisions on my own

70
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:58,960
and that the executives at 3C had no idea.

71
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,040
No way.

72
00:08:03,080 --> 00:08:06,480
We can't let you go to jail.
Right, Te? Right?

73
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,880
There's got to be another way, Dad.

74
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,960
Let's find another way.

75
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:13,400
Please?

76
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:21,680
Can you give me a hug?

77
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,880
Thank you, honey.

78
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:39,760
Thank you for worrying
about a horrible dad like me.

79
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:14,560
This area is being turned
into an entertainment complex.

80
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,360
The payback period
won't take more than two years.

81
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,880
You're really talented, Ms. Giranun.

82
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,840
It's hard to believe
you're new to real estate.

83
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:37,320
Okay, I want to invest with you.

84
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,040
But I want to be the majority shareholder.

85
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:45,560
I want to invest
with you too, Ms. Giranun.

86
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:49,240
If you're investing, don't forget
to ask Fire Phoenix to help you.

87
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,960
They can handle anything for you.

88
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,360
What is Fire Phoenix?

89
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:56,040
What? You really don't know them?

90
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,600
Just mention their name,

91
00:09:57,680 --> 00:10:00,200
and all the big shots are intimidated.

92
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:03,680
Fire Phoenix's leader, called Damon,

93
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:07,680
is being replaced.
The new leader has to have it all.

94
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:11,320
Money, power, and connections.

95
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:19,440
Then, in order to have it all,

96
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,920
you can't just be someone ordinary.

97
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,480
Yes.

98
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:27,000
The next Damon has to be
a businessman in IT

99
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:31,080
who's skilled, rich,
famous, and promising.

100
00:10:31,160 --> 00:10:34,200
Naruban Asawawong.

101
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,680
I tried everything to get you to marry me.

102
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,880
But it turned out you're not Damon.

103
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:51,120
Fortunately, luck was on my side.

104
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:56,480
It allowed me to destroy your 3C

105
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,400
even further.

106
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:13,800
The leader of Fire Phoenix

107
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:16,240
can rule the world

108
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:19,400
or destroy anyone.

109
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:28,160
Die, old man.

110
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:31,240
I will be the new leader of Fire Phoenix.

111
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:37,480
Now, I'll start my revenge on you,

112
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,520
Naruban!

113
00:12:54,160 --> 00:12:58,080
I'll make sure you die
in front of the 3C building,

114
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:02,120
just like how you made my parents die.

115
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,320
If you talk about the virus,

116
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,560
you'll go to jail,

117
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:27,640
and you'll die in jail.

118
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,120
Prin.

119
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:34,080
<i>Chanchai.</i>

120
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,880
I'm getting my karma now.

121
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,720
They must be together somewhere,

122
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:55,440
and they're targeting this place.

123
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:58,680
Where else could Naruban be hiding?

124
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,240
If my guess is correct,

125
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,800
he's got to be at a farm.

126
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:11,960
Either his farm
or his brother's farm nearby.

127
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:20,640
Then, I'll send my men to make sure first,

128
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:23,080
then we'll deal with them.

129
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,720
I really appreciate you and your friends

130
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,760
for helping my family.

131
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:50,080
Right now, only your mother
is still at 3C.

132
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:52,840
How could I possibly stop my mom?

133
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,920
She has the virus.

134
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:58,360
We need to steal it as soon as possible.

135
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:00,440
Is there any way we can do that?

136
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,440
I…

137
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:04,720
I really can't think of anything.

138
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,120
My mom might've moved it somewhere else.

139
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:21,080
Mr. Indhorn said there's a suspicious man

140
00:15:21,160 --> 00:15:22,800
driving around the farm.

141
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:27,040
Could it be one of Punlop's men?

142
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:28,800
I think so.

143
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:32,280
You and your family need to stay here.
Don't go anywhere.

144
00:15:32,920 --> 00:15:36,240
Mr. Indhorn will send workers we can trust
to help take care of you.

145
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,240
Sure.

146
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:50,200
How can we possibly stop your mom?

147
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,960
If she's willing to poison her own son,

148
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:55,560
she's probably got no love left.

149
00:15:55,640 --> 00:15:59,160
Nun, is there anyone at 3C
who can still keep us posted?

150
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,840
I'm organizing a promo for the Hi app.

151
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,760
But you said the project was shelved?

152
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,680
Well, I just changed my mind.

153
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:14,160
And where's Ms. Nun?
She came up with the idea.

154
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:15,560
She's been removed.

155
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,240
Why?

156
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:19,960
It's my orders. Don't ask questions.

157
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:24,120
You shouldn't have an issue with it.
You're an outsider, after all.

158
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,760
You don't even work here.

159
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:29,280
Although I don't work here, I also matter.

160
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,680
After all, I hold
almost as many shares as you.

161
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,080
What's up, Atinuch?

162
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:48,480
Mr. Ryu Dragon's agency just confirmed
he can do the Hi app's promo.

163
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:50,800
He can fly here
for a promo shoot tomorrow.

164
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:58,320
This is none of your business.
Please leave.

165
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:10,240
I want him to do a promo video
somewhere outside.

166
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:14,079
I'll pick the location myself.
No objections.

167
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:16,800
Listen to my orders for everything.

168
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:18,640
Of course.

169
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,280
Yes, Aunt Giranun?

170
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:46,640
Indhorn, can I ask you a favor?

171
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:50,120
I want to shoot my promo video
at your farm.

172
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,440
My farm?

173
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:55,240
Yes. It'll take just one day.

174
00:17:55,880 --> 00:18:00,040
There'll also be a foreign idol
who's a guest at 3C.

175
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:02,400
Sure, Aunt Giranun.

176
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,360
I really appreciate it.

177
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,680
I'll have my secretary
follow up with you on this.

178
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,560
Okay.

179
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:22,840
Ryu Dragon will allow us
to search the farm,

180
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:26,080
both Naruban's farm
and Narumit's farm that's nearby.

181
00:18:28,360 --> 00:18:29,720
We're just hunting Naruban down.

182
00:18:29,800 --> 00:18:32,040
You didn't have to use
Ryu Dragon as an excuse,

183
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,400
not to mention the Hi app's debut.

184
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:37,640
Well, I wanted to mess with their heads,

185
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:41,080
and the best decoy is the virus.

186
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,560
Are you really spreading the virus?

187
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:47,360
No.

188
00:18:48,600 --> 00:18:50,680
It's not time yet.

189
00:19:02,760 --> 00:19:05,560
Fire Phoenix is looking for a way
to spread the virus.

190
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:09,160
They'd spread the virus
at their own event?

191
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:10,800
That'd be far too suspicious.

192
00:19:11,520 --> 00:19:14,400
Lots of people will be infected
before it's even detected.

193
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:18,720
And then, they'll make a profit
selling the vaccines and the cure.

194
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:24,760
We need to hurry and steal the virus.

195
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:30,680
If you enter the 3C building now,

196
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:33,360
you'll end up getting shot
before finding the virus.

197
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,720
I can get you inside.

198
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:38,680
I just don't know
where they're hiding the virus.

199
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:42,200
Naruban's office.

200
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,240
Too simple.

201
00:19:45,320 --> 00:19:48,440
Well, if it's simple, it goes unnoticed.

202
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:55,400
I'll go too.

203
00:19:55,960 --> 00:19:58,880
Don't. The more people we bring,
the higher the risk.

204
00:19:59,840 --> 00:20:01,320
I'll go with Ratee.

205
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:05,920
Be careful once you're inside.

206
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:10,320
If you don't find anything, leave quickly.
Right now, 3C is the most dangerous place.

207
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:19,240
The virus is at 3C?

208
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,360
Come on, look harder.

209
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:41,000
My ring didn't cost just three or four
hundred thousand. It's worth a million.

210
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,520
Rin!

211
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:07,240
Why the hell is she making us
find a ring at this hour?

212
00:22:07,320 --> 00:22:08,880
Yeah. How are we supposed to find it?

213
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:09,960
Exactly.

214
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:18,200
What are you doing here?

215
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:22,080
- What are you doing here?
- The virus is hidden here.

216
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:26,080
- Well, have you found it?
- Not yet.

217
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:30,240
You're looking for
both the virus and Punlop,

218
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:32,920
the man who murdered your father.

219
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:39,000
How did you know?

220
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,480
You're Inspector Phumin's daughter.

221
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:47,560
Rin, you and I share the same goal.

222
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,040
We want to take Fire Phoenix down.

223
00:22:51,080 --> 00:22:52,440
We can help each other.

224
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:58,600
You need to stay alive.

225
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:01,680
Don't sacrifice your life.

226
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:03,640
You still have me.

227
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:19,520
Taiga. Taiga,
are you around here somewhere?

228
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:27,720
Taiga, let's leave.

229
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,440
The cameras are turning back on.
Let's leave now.

230
00:24:11,280 --> 00:24:14,640
You need to stay alive.
Don't sacrifice your life.

231
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,320
You still have me.

232
00:24:21,200 --> 00:24:23,240
The cameras are turning back on.
Let's leave now.

233
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,160
Let me die alone, Taiga,

234
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,440
so you can be with the woman
who loves you.

235
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,960
The virus will rule the world.

236
00:25:06,080 --> 00:25:10,040
People's lives will cost as much
as I want it to be.

237
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:49,440
Thanks.

238
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:55,280
The hell are you doing?

239
00:25:56,560 --> 00:25:58,120
You've gone too far!

240
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:03,360
All of you need to leave. Get out.

241
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:07,520
They're my team. Are you the owner here?

242
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,440
I'm the owner here.

243
00:26:19,120 --> 00:26:21,360
Look, do me a favor.

244
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:24,880
Wrap up the shoot in an hour.

245
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:28,720
No way. I'm here to do my job,

246
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:32,400
so I need to do my best.
An hour isn't enough.

247
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,080
Then, forget about shooting here.

248
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,040
Before you leave,

249
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:41,640
I'd like to search every car
and everyone on your team.

250
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,600
No.

251
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:48,280
Guys, I'm heading to the set now.

252
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,040
Scoot over.

253
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,960
But that's a bomb.

254
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:38,320
Obviously.

255
00:27:39,040 --> 00:27:41,720
If you want money,
I can send it to you right now.

256
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,520
I don't want money.

257
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,760
Scoot over.

258
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,360
Quick.

259
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:52,240
Why would you want to kill me?
Who hired you?

260
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:54,800
Just scoot over.

261
00:28:31,160 --> 00:28:32,000
Quick!

262
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,360
Hey, why don't we just go out
and see for ourselves?

263
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,880
I told you, we can't!

264
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:54,360
If the virus is spread outside,
at least we'll be safe in here.

265
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,280
Aru!

266
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,160
- It's Sun.
- Aru!

267
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:11,080
How's everything? Is everyone okay?

268
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:12,880
How are things outside?

269
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,880
No virus has been spread yet.

270
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:31,920
I know you don't want to die.

271
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:35,560
But it can't be helped.
It just so happened you're here with them.

272
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:38,480
If you have a problem with someone,
just go deal with them.

273
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:40,360
Don't just pick random fights.

274
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:44,880
It's awful. Skilled people
wouldn't do this.

275
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:48,360
Either way, I'm more skilled than you,
and I'm smarter than you.

276
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:50,520
You little baby.

277
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,560
So long, smart-mouth.

278
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:05,400
Rest in peace.

279
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:15,080
It went according to plan.
Taiga and everyone is here.

280
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:17,880
They thought we'd spread the virus
while Ryu Dragon is here.

281
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,800
Please make sure everything's sorted out.

282
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:23,520
Of course. I assure you,

283
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,440
everything will be sorted out.

284
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:07,240
The van driver isn't part of my team.

285
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:09,000
He said if I move,

286
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:11,560
the bomb will go off.

287
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:24,360
Run as fast as you can.

288
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,720
Go.

289
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:35,240
- I'll call the cops.
- It'll be too late.

290
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:48,960
Listen to me, Ryu.

291
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,080
Listen carefully.

292
00:31:53,240 --> 00:31:54,080
We'll risk it.

293
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:57,320
Stand up as I count.

294
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,520
You've got five seconds
before it goes off.

295
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:02,920
Get up and run as far as you can.

296
00:32:05,080 --> 00:32:06,080
You've got this.

297
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:08,960
You two, back off!

298
00:32:10,520 --> 00:32:13,640
I'm right here, Ryu. Let's go together.

299
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:17,520
I told you to back off! Go!

300
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:21,520
We'll sprint away together.
Don't be afraid.

301
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:24,520
Listen to me carefully, Ryu.

302
00:32:24,600 --> 00:32:26,200
I'll say it once again.

303
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,880
I'll count from one to three.

304
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:37,880
One,

305
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:40,680
two,

306
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:42,920
go!

307
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,400
Go!

308
00:32:55,520 --> 00:32:57,200
Are you okay? Are you?

309
00:32:59,040 --> 00:33:00,240
What the hell is going on?

310
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:03,000
You're lucky you're even safe.

311
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:06,280
Easy for you to say.

312
00:33:06,360 --> 00:33:08,680
I deserve to know
what almost took my life.

313
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:10,800
Relax. Can we talk somewhere else?

314
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,160
Why can't we talk here?

315
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:15,520
Because if the bomber returns,
we're all dead!

316
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:18,720
You can't just stand here
asking such silly questions.

317
00:33:29,520 --> 00:33:30,880
What was that noise?

318
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,120
An explosion.

319
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,720
Narumit's farm?

320
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,480
Sun, stay here. I'll go see Taiga.

321
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,400
I had public health professionals
check around here.

322
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:58,280
They didn't find any virus.

323
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:01,240
They weren't planning to spread it here.

324
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:05,040
What virus?

325
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:07,560
Mr. Indhorn,

326
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:12,239
lock down the farm for now
so Mr. Narumit and everyone can stay safe.

327
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,800
Got it.

328
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,400
I'm going to see Mr. Naruban.

329
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:18,840
Don't walk away from me.

330
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:24,360
Tell me. What's going on here?

331
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,840
Why do I have to risk my life
in this place?

332
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:30,320
- It's nothing.
- No, it's not. Take some responsibility.

333
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:33,440
Let me explain.

334
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:37,120
We suspect that someone's
spreading a virus here,

335
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,400
and our farm is in trouble.

336
00:34:46,040 --> 00:34:47,800
Yet you want me to shoot here?

337
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:52,040
Does 3C know about this?

338
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:54,040
3C was the one who asked to shoot here.

339
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,880
Taiga, Taiga.

340
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,920
Khanin.

341
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:07,560
Ryu Dragon. An idol from Hong Kong.

342
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,520
Hong Kong?

343
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:25,960
I don't have time for your stare.

344
00:35:27,080 --> 00:35:29,920
If you keep going quiet on me
and I don't get any answers,

345
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,360
I won't leave this farm.

346
00:35:33,200 --> 00:35:34,160
And I'll tell the police.

347
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,800
Mr. Ryu,

348
00:35:42,720 --> 00:35:46,440
why don't you go shower?

349
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,920
Come on, follow me.

350
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,120
Go.

351
00:35:55,240 --> 00:35:56,840
I'll tell you everything later.

352
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:59,080
- Tell me now.
- Not right now!

353
00:36:25,160 --> 00:36:26,320
What is it, Khanin?

354
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,720
Please make yourself at home.

355
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:48,760
No one's here.

356
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:52,360
My parents are in Bangkok
for a doctor's appointment.

357
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,120
Thanks.

358
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,320
You seem like a good guy.

359
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,720
Thank you.

360
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,560
So who do you think is the bad guy here?

361
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,040
The maniac who drove the van, of course.

362
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:17,080
I'm sorry for everything
that happened today.

363
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:20,720
It's not your fault.
Why are you apologizing?

364
00:37:22,160 --> 00:37:24,440
I'm apologizing as the owner of this farm.

365
00:37:24,520 --> 00:37:27,640
Sorry for giving you bad memories
about this place.

366
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:29,600
I want you to see this place
in a new light.

367
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,440
My farm

368
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:39,400
welcomes you to be here privately.

369
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:44,240
You can come over anytime.
We'll treat you as a VIP guest.

370
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,480
If you'll excuse me.

371
00:38:01,120 --> 00:38:02,000
Hello?

372
00:38:04,160 --> 00:38:05,560
I'm fine.

373
00:38:06,400 --> 00:38:09,240
Tell everyone to tighten the security
at the entrances and exits.

374
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:17,320
And don't forget to tell the locals nearby
to look for the van driver.

375
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:32,120
Naruban said Indhorn's adopted.

376
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:35,920
Were you the one who left
my brother in front of the farm?

377
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,320
Yes.

378
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:41,800
I brought your younger brother
and left him here

379
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:44,160
because I had to hurry and find you.

380
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:47,400
I saw a woman who worked here

381
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:49,200
carry your brother and walk into the farm.

382
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:52,480
At least, it made me certain
that he won't die.

383
00:38:52,560 --> 00:38:55,720
But when I came looking for him again,
everyone said he'd left the farm.

384
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:59,160
A family among the workers
had adopted him and moved out.

385
00:39:01,720 --> 00:39:03,040
But I never expected…

386
00:39:06,680 --> 00:39:09,440
that Narumit would help cover up
the kid's background

387
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:12,360
and raise your brother like his own son.

388
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,000
Indhorn…

389
00:39:21,360 --> 00:39:23,080
Indhorn's my brother?

390
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:31,760
What about my youngest brother, Khanin?

391
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:35,040
You saved him, and where did you put him?

392
00:39:36,280 --> 00:39:37,680
As for your youngest brother,

393
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:42,920
I left him in the care
of Sabaiprae's older sister.

394
00:39:44,360 --> 00:39:46,280
Your mother, Sabaiprae, is half Hong Kong.

395
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:49,000
Her older sister's
a famous celebrity named Wei Bozhi.

396
00:39:51,080 --> 00:39:54,600
After I heard that she left the industry,
she just disappeared.

397
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,600
I tried my hardest,
but I couldn't find her.

398
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:07,160
Ryu Dragon is from Hong Kong.

399
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,760
If he's my brother…

400
00:40:14,160 --> 00:40:15,640
See, Taiga?

401
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:18,360
You have to do whatever you can

402
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:21,920
so that you, Indhorn, and Ryu Dragon
take a DNA test at the same time.

403
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:25,600
That way, you can be sure
that you three are brothers.

404
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:27,280
Not now, Khanin.

405
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:31,280
I can't put my brothers' lives
on the line.

406
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,360
Why?

407
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:35,520
If Fire Phoenix can confirm
the identity of both my brothers,

408
00:40:38,040 --> 00:40:40,280
they'll hunt them down like they used to.

409
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:45,400
You're right. Once we've dealt

410
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:47,840
with Damon, it'll all be over.

411
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:52,600
The three of you will be safe,
and you won't have to cover up anything.

412
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:03,560
That damn Damon's
destroyed my family once.

413
00:41:06,240 --> 00:41:08,120
I won't let him touch my brothers.

414
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:21,920
Someone's there.

415
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:38,160
- Here you go, Mr. Ryu.
- Thank you.

416
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,680
Ryu!

417
00:41:47,160 --> 00:41:48,480
Who are your parents?

418
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:52,880
Hey, why ask about my background
all of a sudden?

419
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:55,680
You can look me up. I'm not just some guy.

420
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:58,120
On social media,

421
00:41:59,320 --> 00:42:01,760
it only says
your mother's a living legend.

422
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:03,480
Wei Bozhi.

423
00:42:04,160 --> 00:42:05,920
But it doesn't say who your father is.

424
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:11,960
Why are you even curious about my father?

425
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:18,800
You may know as much
as I want to share with you.

426
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,360
You're an outsider,

427
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:25,400
yet you're asking about
my personal matters? Learn some manners.

428
00:42:29,000 --> 00:42:30,880
We're not just being rude here.

429
00:42:32,520 --> 00:42:35,560
We have reasons.
Taiga just wants to warn you.

430
00:42:36,720 --> 00:42:37,920
About what?

431
00:42:38,000 --> 00:42:39,480
Watch your back.

432
00:42:40,680 --> 00:42:44,600
- Make sure your family's safe.
- Why?

433
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:47,280
Safe from what? From who?

434
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:53,040
You experienced it firsthand.
You know how dangerous it is.

435
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:56,360
Think I'd be scared
just from what you said?

436
00:42:57,400 --> 00:43:01,320
Well, we can't say much else yet

437
00:43:01,400 --> 00:43:02,680
until everything's sorted out.

438
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:07,600
When the day comes,
you'll get to know everything you need to.

439
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:13,040
My life is mine alone.

440
00:43:13,560 --> 00:43:16,120
Absolutely no one can poke their nose

441
00:43:17,320 --> 00:43:18,440
into my business.

442
00:43:22,840 --> 00:43:23,720
Mr. Ryu,

443
00:43:24,520 --> 00:43:26,720
you should shower
and get changed right away.

444
00:43:27,360 --> 00:43:29,480
I'll have my driver
drive you to the airport.

445
00:43:45,600 --> 00:43:46,880
If you'll excuse me.

446
00:43:51,240 --> 00:43:52,160
Taiga.

447
00:43:53,720 --> 00:43:56,800
One day, they'll both find out

448
00:43:58,360 --> 00:44:01,240
just how much
their older brother loves them

449
00:44:19,440 --> 00:44:20,920
{\an8}Don't do it!

450
00:44:21,000 --> 00:44:22,080
{\an8}<i>Well done, Giranun.</i>

451
00:44:22,160 --> 00:44:25,640
{\an8}From now on, I am Damon.

452
00:44:25,720 --> 00:44:27,560
{\an8}If being brothers means we're all dead,

453
00:44:27,640 --> 00:44:28,880
{\an8}I'd rather be alone.

454
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:31,720
{\an8}Crap! Duck!

455
00:44:31,800 --> 00:44:33,640
{\an8}Mrs. Giranun told me to tell you

456
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:35,360
{\an8}she's taking leave
to look after her husband.

457
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:38,280
{\an8}If you have no business here,
leave the room.

458
00:45:11,520 --> 00:45:13,920
Subtitle translation by:
Ramil Natnitiwitaya

